com.github.sviengine.animation

Class SVIKeyFrameAnimation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.sviengine.animation.SVIAnimation
      • com.github.sviengine.animation.SVIPropertyAnimation
        • com.github.sviengine.animation.SVIKeyFrameAnimation

  • public class SVIKeyFrameAnimation
extends SVIPropertyAnimation
    SVIKeyFrameAnimation Class This Class is make animation use Key frame. you can use key frame time ( 0.0f ~ 1.0f) to control animation Key frame must bigger than past key frame value. (etc. 0.0f -> 0.5f -> 1.0f)
